headline: PG&E (PCG) Stock Short-Circuits in 2025 as Regulatory Risk Sparks Investor Jitters
summary: PG&E Corp (NYSE:PCG) is one of the most oversold S&P 500 stocks so far in 2025. After a relatively better performance in 2024, PG&E stock has been a laggard in 2025 with declines of over 33%, and is now trading near the bottom of its 52-week range.
